        "subject": "LU-9698 osd-ldiskfs: See if kallsyms_lookup_name is exported",
        "message": "LU-9698 osd-ldiskfs: See if kallsyms_lookup_name is exported\n\nkallsyms_lookup_name is not exported prior to 2.6.33 kernels,\nso rhel6 kernels cannot use ldiskfs anymore which annoys\npeople still using it even though it is not supported.\nSo add a configure check for it.\n\nChange-Id: I3a6d54b5dcb09a4a862b0ce08f417acff9f6d9cf\nSigned-off-by: Oleg Drokin <oleg.drokin@intel.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
